    "action_carousel_card_id",
    "action_carousel_card_name",
    "action_converted_product_id",
    "action_reaction",
    "standard_event_content_type"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "`breakdowns` and `action_breakdowns` may be combined; some pairs are invalid (e.g. impression_device + publisher_platform cross-breakdowns) — the API will reject invalid combinations with error code 100.",
    "`attribution_setting` controls the attribution window; default is the ad account's default setting.",
    "`quality_ranking`, `engagement_rate_ranking`, `conversion_rate_ranking` require ads with sufficient delivery (typically 500+ impressions over the last 7 days).",
    "This catalog is a snapshot. For the authoritative current list, see the Meta Marketing API docs or call Meta's own field-introspection endpoints."
  ]
}
